Name: Crunch Time! Beat the Clock
About the game: A short dissertation project, please enjoy for what it is. Crunch Time! Beat The Clock is a third-person action platformer. Jump, Fight and Blast your way through a variety of levels in order to beat the clock once and for all! Time is finite, though you can regain it at the exchange of your health, so be careful where you step.
